372
00:29:02,637 --> 00:29:08,457
♫  You are like the flowers and moon, 
 more graceful than a palace in the sky  ♫

373
00:29:08,457 --> 00:29:09,735
My Lord.

374
00:29:09,736 --> 00:29:11,276
What is this?

375
00:29:14,335 --> 00:29:17,195
I gave you a mole that brings bad luck to your husband.

376
00:29:17,195 --> 00:29:19,876
Let's see who dares to covet you from now on.

377
00:29:21,095 --> 00:29:22,334
 My Lord. 

378
00:29:22,335 --> 00:29:24,935
 Official Xu, Minister of Revenue, wants to see you. 

379
00:29:28,176 --> 00:29:30,696
Please have mercy, My Lord!

380
00:29:31,456 --> 00:29:33,435
I was wrong.

381
00:29:36,176 --> 00:29:37,776
Were you?

382
00:29:38,496 --> 00:29:41,435
Do you know what you did wrong?

383
00:29:41,435 --> 00:29:47,516
I... I was wrong for... for...

384
00:29:47,516 --> 00:29:49,614
You are greedy and cowardly.

385
00:29:49,615 --> 00:29:50,935
You have a glib tongue.

386
00:29:50,936 --> 00:29:53,616
Bold as brass. Lack foresight.

387
00:29:55,615 --> 00:29:57,094
There's more.

388
00:29:57,095 --> 00:30:02,195
You acted in bad faith and went around attracting bad admirers.

389
00:30:04,375 --> 00:30:07,815
What? Bad admirers?

390
00:30:12,235 --> 00:30:17,835
Anyway, go back now and reflect on yourself.

391
00:30:20,295 --> 00:30:23,136
Yes, My Lord. I shall take my leave.

392
00:30:34,055 --> 00:30:35,534
My Lord,

393
00:30:35,535 --> 00:30:39,375
was it that bad?

394
00:30:41,035 --> 00:30:42,435
Yes.

395
00:30:43,375 --> 00:30:45,315
He's so petty.

396
00:30:45,315 --> 00:30:47,194
A mole that brings bad luck to my husband?

397
00:30:47,194 --> 00:30:49,236
Aren't you jinxing yourself?

398
00:30:52,055 --> 00:30:53,215
He was furious?

399
00:30:53,216 --> 00:30:54,616
Yes.

400
00:30:54,616 --> 00:30:56,429
Think of something.

401
00:30:58,095 --> 00:30:59,595
Official Mu.

402
00:31:00,375 --> 00:31:01,775
Official Mu,

403
00:31:01,775 --> 00:31:04,976
we heard about what happened this morning.

404
00:31:04,976 --> 00:31:10,195
Though we haven't worked together for long, all of us truly admire your abilities.

405
00:31:10,195 --> 00:31:13,735
How could you be so careless and end up offending Lord Ding?

406
00:31:13,735 --> 00:31:16,816
I... I find it strange.

407
00:31:18,016 --> 00:31:21,035
Could it be because you kowtowed a whole day two days go just

408
00:31:21,035 --> 00:31:24,095
to have him approve all the Ministry of Revenue documents?

409
00:31:24,095 --> 00:31:26,516
And that upset him?

410
00:31:27,896 --> 00:31:28,814
Exactly.

411
00:31:28,815 --> 00:31:33,136
I talked back to him that day so that I could get all the documents

412
00:31:33,136 --> 00:31:35,336
for the Ministry of Revenue.

413
00:31:36,216 --> 00:31:39,294
I guess I am getting my retribution today.

414
00:31:39,295 --> 00:31:41,776
And I am panicking now.

415
00:31:41,776 --> 00:31:46,516
I just hope Lord Ding will forgive me and show mercy.

416
00:31:47,496 --> 00:31:49,196
That's our fault.

417
00:31:49,216 --> 00:31:50,895
It's our fault!

418
00:31:50,895 --> 00:31:52,436
I'm sorry.

419
00:31:53,696 --> 00:31:56,114
Official Li, I need to be alone for a while.

420
00:31:56,114 --> 00:31:57,876
Please excuse me.

421
00:32:03,115 --> 00:32:05,375
I feel bad for Official Mu.

422
00:32:05,375 --> 00:32:06,675
Yes.

423
00:32:08,396 --> 00:32:10,115
It's not easy for her.

424
00:32:10,115 --> 00:32:12,135
Let's go, Official Li.

425
00:32:20,236 --> 00:32:23,836
Uncle, I thought you'd always admired Mu Zhuohua.

426
00:32:23,836 --> 00:32:26,015
Why did you criticize her so badly this time?

427
00:32:26,016 --> 00:32:27,935
What did she do wrong?

428
00:32:27,935 --> 00:32:30,816
You caught wind of it so quickly.

429
00:32:30,816 --> 00:32:32,395
That's for sure.

430
00:32:32,395 --> 00:32:35,835
After all, she and I have gone through thick and thin before.

431
00:32:35,835 --> 00:32:38,916
It's normal that I am concerned about her.

432
00:32:38,916 --> 00:32:43,256
It was just a business trip to Jiangnan.

433
00:32:43,256 --> 00:32:45,515
That's barely thick and thin.

434
00:32:45,515 --> 00:32:47,536
How is it not?

435
00:32:47,536 --> 00:32:51,156
You see. The days we spent on disaster relief were tough days.

436
00:32:51,156 --> 00:32:54,176
Returning to the capital and being rewarded were good days.

437
00:32:57,635 --> 00:33:01,615
Uncle, you haven't answered me.

438
00:33:01,615 --> 00:33:05,216
You always admired Mu Zhuohua's talents.

439
00:33:05,216 --> 00:33:08,596
Why are you giving her a hard time now?

440
00:33:10,435 --> 00:33:14,315
When young people have made a bit of achievements,

441
00:33:14,315 --> 00:33:18,155
they become impetuous and careless.

442
00:33:18,155 --> 00:33:20,456
I must humble her.

443
00:33:23,276 --> 00:33:27,916
Uncle, I'm sure it was just a careless mistake.

444
00:33:27,916 --> 00:33:30,516
Don't be so hard on her.

445
00:33:30,516 --> 00:33:33,696
I heard that she cried after getting scolded by you.

446
00:33:42,096 --> 00:33:44,735
Why are you looking at me like this?

447
00:33:44,735 --> 00:33:49,976
Chen'er, you are 21 now, no?

448
00:33:50,836 --> 00:33:52,916
At the palace banquet back then,

449
00:33:52,916 --> 00:33:55,596
was there any young lady that caught your eye?

450
00:33:55,596 --> 00:33:59,116
His Majesty can arrange the marriage for you.

451
00:33:59,116 --> 00:34:03,116
Uncle, stop making fun of me.

452
00:34:03,116 --> 00:34:07,995
Are these noble young ladies out of their minds?

453
00:34:07,995 --> 00:34:09,955
I have avoided them so hard,

454
00:34:09,955 --> 00:34:12,535
but they still keep coming to me.

455
00:34:18,376 --> 00:34:20,675
It is not that they are foolish.

456
00:34:20,675 --> 00:34:24,295
It is that their families are crafty.

457
00:34:25,975 --> 00:34:28,334
This won't do. It's terrifying.

458
00:34:28,334 --> 00:34:30,875
I can't even have a meal at ease.

459
00:34:32,115 --> 00:34:35,636
I must find a way to end it once and for all.

460
00:34:37,896 --> 00:34:41,436
To be honest, if it were Mu Zhuohua,

461
00:34:41,436 --> 00:34:44,136
I think I can accept that.

462
00:34:52,195 --> 00:34:56,676
Uncle, why are you staring at me like that again?

463
00:34:56,676 --> 00:34:58,556
She's not for you.

464
00:34:58,556 --> 00:35:00,735
I know that.

465
00:35:00,735 --> 00:35:05,975
Mother and Grandmother have been nagging at me since the coming-of-age ceremony.

466
00:35:05,975 --> 00:35:09,635
They said I must marry a noble daughter as the Princess Consort.

467
00:35:09,635 --> 00:35:12,376
But I don't like it.

468
00:35:12,376 --> 00:35:15,915
Just like you, Uncle. You have remained unmarried.

469
00:35:15,915 --> 00:35:19,616
It's because you refuse to be controlled by these noble families.

470
00:35:19,616 --> 00:35:22,935
If I don't marry, I won't have an heir.

471
00:35:22,935 --> 00:35:28,016
To some people, it is a good thing.

472
00:35:35,035 --> 00:35:37,275
Do you have it ready?

473
00:35:38,476 --> 00:35:42,516
Look. Just fresh out of the bank.

474
00:35:47,676 --> 00:35:50,095
She just got scolded by Uncle.

475
00:35:50,095 --> 00:35:52,156
She must be upset.

476
00:35:52,156 --> 00:35:55,015
If she sees this, she will cheer up for sure.

477
00:35:55,016 --> 00:35:56,516
Come on.

478
00:35:58,856 --> 00:36:01,536
What are you waiting for? Let's go.

479
00:36:01,536 --> 00:36:03,355
Yes, Your Highness.

480
00:36:12,435 --> 00:36:14,676
Greetings, Your Highness.

481
00:36:14,676 --> 00:36:16,896
Have you seen Ms. Mu?

482
00:36:16,896 --> 00:36:19,115
Ms. Mu left very early today.

483
00:36:19,115 --> 00:36:23,056
She said she was going to dine with Official Shen at Xiaoqin Pleasure House.

484
00:36:23,056 --> 00:36:25,195
Xiaoqin Pleasure House again?

485
00:36:28,376 --> 00:36:31,856
She invited Jinghong but not me.

486
00:36:34,376 --> 00:36:36,176
Your Highness.

487
00:36:36,995 --> 00:36:39,376
I've finally found you.

488
00:36:39,376 --> 00:36:41,475
His Majesty has summoned you to Wende Hall

489
00:36:41,475 --> 00:36:44,856
to discuss your visit to the temporary imperial residence.

490
00:36:56,695 --> 00:36:57,725
Let's go.

491
00:36:57,726 --> 00:37:00,078
   

492
00:37:10,276 --> 00:37:13,395
Brother Sun, what are you doing?

493
00:37:13,395 --> 00:37:16,236
Recently, Yunyun has acted out of line

494
00:37:16,236 --> 00:37:18,916
and caused you a lot of trouble.

495
00:37:18,916 --> 00:37:22,596
I feel really sorry.

496
00:37:22,596 --> 00:37:26,655
I apologize to you on my sister's behalf.

497
00:37:26,655 --> 00:37:28,276
Brother Sun, you don't have to do this.

498
00:37:28,276 --> 00:37:30,236
I'm not someone who'd take it out on others.

499
00:37:30,236 --> 00:37:32,455
I'm too ashamed to face you.

500
00:37:32,455 --> 00:37:34,535
She is she and you are you.

501
00:37:34,535 --> 00:37:37,276
Besides, she has left the Ministry of Revenue.

502
00:37:37,276 --> 00:37:39,716
It's water under the bridge now.

503
00:37:41,735 --> 00:37:45,035
- Come on, Brother Sun. 
 - All right. Stop standing there.

504
00:37:45,035 --> 00:37:46,935
We are at a place of entertainment.

505
00:37:46,935 --> 00:37:49,396
Let's just talk about entertaining things.

506
00:37:49,396 --> 00:37:52,015
- Come on. Sit down. 
 - He's right.

507
00:37:53,075 --> 00:37:56,996
- Brother Shen, let's drink to Brother Sun. 
 - Sure. Good.

508
00:37:56,996 --> 00:38:00,435
Then I shall drink to you two as well.

509
00:38:05,756 --> 00:38:09,155
Come on, we are not done drinking.

510
00:38:09,155 --> 00:38:11,376
- Drink up, Brother Sun. 
 - Carry on.

511
00:38:19,416 --> 00:38:23,276
I knew you two would quickly rise through the ranks.

512
00:38:23,276 --> 00:38:25,616
One is the Director of the Ministry of Revenue.

513
00:38:25,616 --> 00:38:28,275
Another one is the Director of the Ministry of Personnel.

514
00:38:29,976 --> 00:38:35,196
Among those from our batch, you two are the quickest to rise!

515
00:38:37,515 --> 00:38:40,355
All right, Brother Sun. Don't be self-deprecating.

516
00:38:40,355 --> 00:38:42,295
You have true talent and knowledge, too.

517
00:38:42,296 --> 00:38:47,276
You would've been successful like us if you hadn't been burdened by your family.

518
00:38:47,276 --> 00:38:52,936
Brother Shen, are you talking about Jiangzuo?

519
00:38:53,816 --> 00:38:57,996
The Sun family already has Consort Shu and Minister of Works.

520
